query_string: SELECT t.title, t.production_year FROM title t WHERE t.production_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005 AND t.kind_id = 1 ORDER BY t.production_year DESC LIMIT 100;
SELECT n.name, n.gender FROM name n WHERE n.gender = 'f' AND n.name_pcode_cf = 'ANR' ORDER BY n.name LIMIT 100;
SELECT ci.person_id, ci.role_id FROM cast_info ci JOIN title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id WHERE t.production_year = 1999 AND ci.role_id IN (1, 2, 3) LIMIT 100;
SELECT mk.movie_id, k.keyword FROM movie_keyword mk JOIN keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id WHERE k.keyword LIKE 'based-on-novel%' ORDER BY mk.movie_id DESC LIMIT 100;
SELECT mi.movie_id, mi.info FROM movie_info_idx mi WHERE mi.info_type_id = 112 ORDER BY mi.movie_id LIMIT 100;
